  "text": "Understanding the Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix season schedule will let you know when your favorite Chapter 2 map will return to Fortnite and what musical icon will be featured that week.Starting with Seasons 1 and 2, the map will be updated each week to the next season (or two) in order, before concluding with Season 8, starting on Nov. 21. But this throwback season is a bit different, with the Chapter 2 seasons remixed (hey, that’s the name!) in honor of a different musician who appears as a boss.As with Fortnite OG — though this is a shorter, month-long season — there’s still a Battle Pass to purchase, with mashups of Chapter 2 skins to unlock.Each update will also introduce many of those season’s items, weapons, and vehicles to complete the trip down memory lane. Here’s when you can expect each week in Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix, and when Fortnite Remix ends.And for a look at everything coming this season, see our guide on what’s new in Fortnite Remix.Table of ContentsFortnite Remix season schedule datesWhat time does the season update go live in Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix?Fortnite Remix Week 1Fortnite Remix Week 2Fortnite Remix Week 3Fortnite Remix Week 4When does Fortnite Remix end?Fortnite Remix season schedule datesBefore we go week-by-week and season-by-season, here’s the complete Fortnite Remix season schedule at a glance:Nov. 2 to Nov. 7: Snoop Dogg, TNTina, and MeowdasNov. 7 to Nov. 14: EminemNov. 14 to Nov. 21: Ice SpiceNov. 21 to Nov. 28: Juice WRLDNov 30: Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix endsWhat follows is what has been confirmed to be added to Fortnite Remix so far, with developer Epic saying items could be remain for the entire season, or only stay for that given week. We’ll find out exactly what is available when each week’s hotfix arrives.What time does the season update go live in Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix?Each Thursday, the current Fortnite Remix season will change at (or around) the following time:6 a.m. PST for the West Coast of North America9 a.m. EST for the East Coast of North America2 p.m. GMT for the U.K.3 p.m. CEST for west mainland Europe11 p.m. JST in JapanFortnite Remix Week 1Image: Epic GamesDuring Week 1, the Agency compound in the center of the map becomes the Doggpound where you can face off against none other than Snoop Dogg. Defeating him will get you the Snoop’s Drum Gun Mythic.Elsewhere, Meowdas and his Peow Peow Rifle are at The Yacht in the northeast and TNTina with her Ka-Boom Bow are at The Rig in the southwest.Fortnite Remix Week 2Image: Epic GamesWeek 2 adds a new POI, Spaghetti Grotto, where you’ll find Eminem and his Mythic RG Minigun.Fortnite Remix Week 3Image: Epic GamesFor Week 3, Shark Isle becomes Ice Isle with the arrival of Ice Spice. Defeat her to get both the Ice Spice’s Grappler and Ice Spice’s Rifle Mythics.Fortnite Remix Week 4Image: Epic GamesNot much has been released about what Week 4 will look like, but the performer being honored is Juice WRLD.When does Fortnite Remix end?Image: Epic GamesFortnite Chapter 2 Remix will end on Saturday, Nov. 30, with another live event.The event is scheduled for:11 a.m. PST for the West Coast of North America2 p.m. EST for the East Coast of North America7 p.m. GMT for the U.K.8 p.m. CEST for west mainland Europe4 a.m. JST on Dec. 1 in JapanThis not the first time a Fortnite season has ended on a Saturday, and based on those other weekend finales, Sunday, Dec. 1, is likely when the new season will go live.",
  "image": "https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-battle-royale-chapter-2-remix-1_d992d7.jpg?quality=90\u0026strip=all\u0026crop=42.4,2.2517452006981,57.6,95.496509598604",
  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"zephr-anchor\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnderstanding the \u003cstrong\u003eFortnite Chapter 2 Remix season schedule \u003c/strong\u003ewill let you know when your favorite Chapter 2 map will return to \u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/fortnite-battle-royale/40155\"\u003eFortnite\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e and what musical icon will be featured that week.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eStarting with Seasons 1 and 2, the map will be updated each week to the next season (or two) in order, before concluding with Season 8, starting on Nov. 21. But this throwback season is a bit different, with the Chapter 2 seasons remixed (hey, that’s the name!) in honor of a different musician who appears as a boss.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs with Fortnite OG — though this is a shorter, month-long season — there’s still a Battle Pass to purchase, with mashups of Chapter 2 skins to unlock.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach update will also introduce many of those season’s items, weapons, and vehicles to complete the trip down memory lane. Here’s when you can expect each week in Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix, and when Fortnite Remix ends.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd for a look at everything coming this season, see our guide on \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/473872\"\u003ewhat’s new in Fortnite Remix\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cnav\u003e\u003ch2\u003eTable of Contents\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#bHtcRy\"\u003eFortnite Remix season schedule dates\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#St1FJ5\"\u003eWhat time does the season update go live in Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#ArrQG7\"\u003eFortnite Remix Week 1\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#ojsOpb\"\u003eFortnite Remix Week 2\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#HEPDq6\"\u003eFortnite Remix Week 3\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#4SNIwk\"\u003eFortnite Remix Week 4\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#cQ0gDG\"\u003eWhen does Fortnite Remix end?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/nav\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"bHtcRy\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFortnite Remix season schedule dates\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eBefore we go week-by-week and season-by-season, here’s the complete Fortnite Remix season schedule at a glance:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNov. 2 to Nov. 7: \u003c/strong\u003eSnoop Dogg, TNTina, and Meowdas\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNov. 7 to Nov. 14: \u003c/strong\u003eEminem\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNov. 14 to Nov. 21: \u003c/strong\u003eIce Spice\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNov. 21 to Nov. 28: \u003c/strong\u003eJuice WRLD\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNov 30:\u003c/strong\u003e Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix ends\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhat follows is what has been confirmed to be added to Fortnite Remix so far, with developer Epic saying items could be remain for the entire season, or only stay for that given week. We’ll find out exactly what is available when each week’s hotfix arrives.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"St1FJ5\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat time does the season update go live in Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach Thursday, the current Fortnite Remix season will change at (or around) the following time:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e6 a.m. PST\u003c/strong\u003e for the West Coast of North America\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e9 a.m. EST\u003c/strong\u003e for the East Coast of North America\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e2 p.m. GMT\u003c/strong\u003e for the U.K.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3 p.m. CEST\u003c/strong\u003e for west mainland Europe\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e11 p.m. JST\u003c/strong\u003e in Japan\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"ArrQG7\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFortnite Remix Week 1\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-snoop-dogg-1920.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix Snoop Dogg\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-snoop-dogg-1920.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-snoop-dogg-1920.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-snoop-dogg-1920.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-