.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-snoop-dogg-1920.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-snoop-dogg-1920.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Epic Games\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eDuring Week 1, the Agency compound in the center of the map becomes the Doggpound where you can face off against none other than \u003cstrong\u003eSnoop Dogg\u003c/strong\u003e. Defeating him will get you the \u003cstrong\u003eSnoop’s Drum Gun\u003c/strong\u003e Mythic.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eElsewhere, \u003cstrong\u003eMeowdas\u003c/strong\u003e and his \u003cstrong\u003ePeow Peow Rifle\u003c/strong\u003e are at The Yacht in the northeast and \u003cstrong\u003eTNTina \u003c/strong\u003ewith her \u003cstrong\u003eKa-Boom Bow\u003c/strong\u003e are at The Rig in the southwest.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"ojsOpb\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFortnite Remix Week 2\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-spaghetti-grott.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix Eminem’s Mom’s Spaghetti restaurant\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/si